Caitlyn Jenner and Candis Cayne were spotted sneaking out of the backdoor of Craigs after enjoying a dinner date on on June 22. As Star readers know, the pair grew close on Jenner’s reality show I Am Cait before its cancellation, and were even rumored to be dating.

Watch the video above and don’t forget to subscribe to our YouTube Channel!
